title: Late Night Tortilla Jian Bing
description: A quick cheaty version of a classic Chinese street snack, using a tortilla in place of a crepe. Fry some chiles and scallion whites, add an egg beaten with some chopped cilantro and scallion greens, then spread it into a single, thin omelet and press a tortilla directly on top so that it sticks. Carefully flip it all over egg-side-up, then brush with hoisin sauce and chile oil, add more fresh aromatics, fold it up, and eat. You can add black sesame, fried tofu skin, ham, chopped bacon or sausage, etc.
